body:
Hey everyone! This is a reboot of my previous version of this. I thought why not do this again! With the name changes, one person's name can be misspelled a plethora of times (Yay! ^-^) So this is why I'm deciding to bring it back.

Old Post: https://avicus.net/forums/e6c16406f

The point of this is so that you reply with misspelled or altered versions of your own username. They can be from previous names you had. (Preferably funny and ridiculous misspells/alterations) So... go ahead and slaughter spelling in the English language!

Kammy878: kimmy, spammy878 spermy kamy

Frustration: Frust Frusty Frustation

Kleypex: None as of yet


Have Fun!
